{
  "stem": "12337.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and I remember one thing, that the minute the Germans would come looking for the-- you know, for Jews in the farm, the first thing I would do is put on my shoes.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was like obsessed with my shoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had high-- high boots, like.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I used to start lacing them up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was afraid if they catch us, I won't have time to put on my shoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They're going to get angry at me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They're going to hit me, because they have to wait for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was ready.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The minute the Germans came on the farm, my shoes were on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I started tying up my shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so afterwards, he took us out from there, and he took-- put us in the barn.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He had a barn, you know, where you can put like horses and-- in the middle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was hay on each side of the barn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he made us a hole in one of they hay-- you know, in-- in the hay.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And slowly, but surely, we stayed there for 18 months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And every few days, we were going to leave.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was-- told us to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I can't blame him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He said, you know, tomorrow, it's going to be better, the weather.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he knew that the minute that he would let us go, we would be killed within maybe hours, not even days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was a party that was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I'm not sure if you've ever heard this word-- Ukrainian that called themselves [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were worse than Hitler, worse than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They said a bullet was too good for a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When they would catch Jews, they would just cut them up to pieces.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
